    { question: "What exactly is AI Google Business Profile optimization for tradesmen?", answer: "It\'s an AI-powered service designed for skilled tradespeople who are too busy doing their trade to manage their Google presence. Your Google Business Profile (formerly Google My Business / GMB) is the listing that appears when customers search for your trade on Google Maps and Google Search. AI optimization manages this listing for you — configuring it with trade-specific categories, automating review requests via SMS and WhatsApp after every completed job, responding to reviews professionally, and maintaining the ongoing engagement that Google\'s local algorithm rewards with higher visibility. Whether you\'re a plumber, electrician, builder, roofer, or any other tradesperson, the system is configured for your specific trade and service area. The AI works in the background while you work on-site, building the online reputation that keeps your diary full." },
