 },
    { question: "How does AI review generation work for tradesmen?", answer: "It\'s straightforward: finish a job, and the AI texts your customer a friendly review request via SMS or WhatsApp. The message thanks them, references the work done, and includes a one-tap link to your Google review page. The timing is calibrated to your trade — emergency repairs trigger requests quickly (while gratitude is highest), while larger or planned work waits until the customer has fully appreciated the result. You don\'t need to remember to ask, you don\'t need to hand anyone a card, you don\'t need to send awkward follow-up messages. The AI handles it all. Reviews that mention specific work — the actual job you did, in the customer\'s own words — are the most powerful content on Google for attracting similar jobs." },
